## Class Naming Convention

### The Rule

All design-system component classes use the `rux-` prefix. Application-specific
components (things that only exist in this app) do not require a prefix.

Structure follows BEM:

```
.rux-{block}                  Block  — the component itself
.rux-{block}__{element}       Element — a part of the component
.rux-{block}--{modifier}      Modifier — a variant or state
```

### Patterns at a glance

| Pattern | When to use | Examples |
|---------|-------------|---------|
| `.rux-{name}` | Any reusable DS component | `.rux-card`, `.rux-modal`, `.rux-btn` |
| `.rux-{name}__{part}` | A named sub-part of a component | `.rux-card__body`, `.rux-modal__header` |
| `.rux-{name}--{variant}` | A visual variant or size | `.rux-card--compact`, `.rux-btn--danger` |
| `.is-{state}` | JS-toggled boolean state | `.is-hidden`, `.is-open`, `.is-active`, `.is-empty` |
| `.has-{state}` | JS-toggled compound state | `.has-error`, `.has-progress` |
| *(no prefix)* | App-specific, non-reusable | `.schedule-grid`, `.trip-bar`, `.bus-assign` |

### Design-system vs. app-specific

**Use `rux-` prefix** for anything that could exist in a different app:
cards, modals, buttons, headers, panels, badges, accordions, menus, form grids.

**No prefix required** for things only this app has:
the schedule grid, trip bars, bus assignment layout, agenda header, waiting list.

### State classes stay unprefixed

`.is-*` and `.has-*` are added and removed by JavaScript. They are universal enough
that namespacing them would add noise without benefit. Never create `.rux-is-*`.

### Migration targets

These existing classes violate the convention and should be renamed when each
component is next edited. Every rename requires a find-replace across
`css/`, `index.html`, and `js/app.js`.

| Current (violation) | Target | Home file |
|---------------------|--------|-----------|
| `.c-card`, `.c-card--compact`, `.c-card__body` | `.rux-card` | `surfaces.css` |
| `.c-header`, `.c-header__title`, `.c-header__actions` | `.rux-header` | `surfaces.css` |
| `.heading-1` | `.rux-heading` | `surfaces.css` |
| `.nav-controls` | `.rux-nav` | `surfaces.css` |
| `.cds-accordion`, `.cds-accordion__*` | `.rux-accordion` | `primitives.css` |
| `.modal`, `.modal__card`, `.modal__body` | `.rux-modal` | `modals.css` |
| `.badge` | `.rux-badge` | `primitives.css` |
| `.o-app-layout`, `.o-app-layout__*` | `.rux-app-layout` | `layout.css` |
| `.form-section-card` | `.rux-form-section` | `form.css` |
| `.context-menu` | `.rux-context-menu` | `base.css` |
| `.dropdown__menu` | `.rux-menu` | `base.css` / `dropdown.css` |

