## Quick Reference — Token Flow

```
oklch(50% 0.2 260)          ← literal value
       ↓
--rux-color-blue             ← Tier 1  (variables.css)
       ↓
--rux-bg-2                   ← Tier 2  (variables.css)
       ↓
--rux-fld-bg                 ← Tier 3  (form.css :root)
       ↓
background: var(--rux-fld-bg) ← component CSS rule
```
